.TH man 1 "AUG 18 2023" "Holberton Simple Shell"

.SH NAME
    hsh - Holberton Simple Shell: command line interpreter

.SH SYNOPSIS
hsh [filename]

.SH DESCRIPTION
    .B hsh
    is a basic imitation of a command line interpreter tat reads and implements basic commands from user input,
    functioning similarly to a shell.
.PP
    .B hsh
    is compiled on Ubuntu 20.04 LTS with gcc and is designed to run in both interactive and non-interactive modes.
.PP
.SH USER input
    When a user enters a command and presses Enter, the shell performs the following actions:

    1. Divides the command into a set of words.

    2. Searches for the entered command.

    3. Executes the command.
.PP
.SH COMMAND SEARCH
    When searching for a command, the shell first checks if it is a built-in command.
    If a built-in command is not found, the shell looks for the commmand in the PATH.
.PP
.SH BUILT-IT commands
    .IP help
    Displays the shell's help.
    .IP exit
    Terminates the process and frees allocated memory.
    .IP cd
    Changes the crurrent directory.

.SH ISSUES
    Currently, there are issues with the functioning of the Tab and Enter combination.

